Package: IBRAP
Type: Package
Title: Integrated Benchmarking scRNA-seq Analytical Pipeline (IBRAP)
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Connor Harry Knight
Maintainer: The package maintainer <c.h.knight@qmul.ac.uk>
Description: This package integrates numerous leading scRNA-seq analytical components
    into one major framework. These components can all be applied to the dataset or
    you can stick to one pipeline. If numerous have been generated, benchmarking
    metrices can be applied to ascertain which pipeline performed best. A tutorial
    on how to use IBRAP can be found at: https://github.com/connorhknight/IBRAP
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
